{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Show Selected Item Count in help Display if any items are selected\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is a lighttweight utility meant to be left running in the background. When media items are selected, it temporarily replaces the info display text below the TCP with a live count of the selected items.\par}
}

